WEBVTT

00:06:26.608 --> 00:06:31.056
wrote on his blog
about a previous mass murderer,

00:06:31.080 --> 00:06:32.917
saying,

00:06:32.941 --> 00:06:36.747
"I've noticed that people like him

00:06:36.771 --> 00:06:39.652
are all alone and unknown,

00:06:39.676 --> 00:06:42.196
but when they spill a little blood,

00:06:42.220 --> 00:06:45.144
the whole world knows who they are."

00:06:45.881 --> 00:06:51.537
A man who was known by no one
is now known by everyone,

00:06:51.561 --> 00:06:55.642
his face splashed across every screen,

00:06:55.666 --> 00:06:57.452
his name on the lips

00:06:57.476 --> 00:06:59.628
of everyone on the planet,